# perf_stress.shot — M6 P03 heavy bench, "no cap" baseline.
#
# Loads citadel (the largest authored map: 12 grapple anchors, ACID,
# WIND, 31 pickups, 100+ tiles wide). 10 extra chassis fill the view.
# Local mech runs Heavy + Burst jetpack and sustains the jet hold so
# the BURST-class plume is on every frame, exercising the worst-case
# halftone+shimmer fragment cost.
#
# This is the bench that actually loads the GPU. Pair with the
# perf_stress_capped variant for the A/B.

window 3440 1440
seed   3 7
out    build/shots/perf_stress
map    citadel
loadout Heavy "Mass Driver" "Frag Grenades" Heavy Burst

internal_h 0
perf_overlay on

extra_chassis Heavy    1600 900
extra_chassis Scout    1900 900
extra_chassis Sniper   2200 900
extra_chassis Engineer 2500 900
extra_chassis Trooper  2800 900
extra_chassis Heavy    3100 900

aim 2000 900

# Sustain the jet through the whole run so the plume fires every
# tick and the shimmer hot zone stays in the uniform array.
at 30 press jet
at 580 release jet

at  60 shot t060
at 180 shot t180
at 300 shot t300
at 420 shot t420
at 540 shot t540
at 600 end
